<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Share Your Mang Crinkle Experience</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #292524;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    
    /* Admin Container - matching admin design system */
    .admin-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .admin-container-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .admin-container-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .admin-container-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .admin-container-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    
    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .content-section p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    /* Order Details */
    .order-details {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .order-details-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .order-detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
    }
    
    .order-detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .order-detail-label {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .order-detail-value {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    /* Review Benefits */
    .review-benefits {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .review-benefits h3 {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .review-benefits ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .review-benefits li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #ea580c;
    }
    
    /* Admin Button - matching admin-btn-primary with correct hover */
    .admin-btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f54900;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #ca3500;
    }
    
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="admin-container">
      <div class="admin-container-header">
        <div class="brand-logo">Mang Crinkle</div>
        <h1 class="admin-container-title">How Was Your Experience?</h1>
        <p class="admin-container-subtitle">We'd love to hear your thoughts, <%= @customer_name %>!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-container-content">
        <div class="content-section">
          <p>Hello <%= @customer_name %>,</p>
          
          <p>We hope you've had a chance to enjoy your recent Mang Crinkle order! Your experience matters deeply to us, and we'd love to hear about it.</p>
          
          <div class="order-details">
            <div class="order-details-title">Your Recent Order</div>
            
            <div class="order-detail-row">
              <span class="order-detail-label">Order Number:</span>
              <span class="order-detail-value">#<%= @order.id %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-detail-row">
              <span class="order-detail-label">Order Date:</span>
              <span class="order-detail-value"><%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-detail-row">
              <span class="order-detail-label">Items:</span>
              <span class="order-detail-value"><%= @order.line_items.count %> item<%= @order.line_items.count == 1 ? '' : 's' %></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-section">
            <p>As a small family business, every review helps us improve and helps other Filipino food lovers discover our authentic treats. Whether you loved your order or have suggestions for us, we genuinely value your feedback.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="review-benefits">
            <h3>Why Your Review Matters:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Helps us maintain our quality standards</li>
              <li>Guides other customers in their choices</li>
              <li>Supports our small family business</li>
              <li>Helps us improve our recipes and service</li>
              <li>Builds our community of Filipino food lovers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-section">
            <p>It only takes a few minutes to share your experience, and it means the world to us. Click below to leave your review:</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.new_order_review_url(@order, host: Rails.application.config.action_mailer.default_url_options[:host]) %>" class="admin-btn-primary">Leave a Review</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-section">
            <p>Thank you for choosing Mang Crinkle and for being part of our family. We're grateful for customers like you who help us share the joy of authentic Filipino treats!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>This review invitation was sent for order #<%= @order.id %></p>
          <p>Questions? Reply to this email or contact us at <%= company_email %></p>
          
          <div class="signature">
            <p>With love and fresh-baked goodness,<br>
            <span class="signature-name">The Mang Crinkle Team</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 